{"actor":"Ivar Abrahamsen","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-07-03T13:43:29Z","event_type":"updated","id":"e13ae479-a61c-4cce-9353-b74012fe9d68","issue_id":"bad_usernames_api-au3","new_value":"{\"description\":\"Use CircleCI (house default across the letterbox fleet; GH Actions only on the 2 newest repos, gauge + sortingoffice). Base on letterbox-scoring/.circleci/config.yml but trim to a single 'build' job for this repo's current scope:\\n- image: sbtscala/scala-sbt:eclipse-temurin-* matching sbt 1.10.7 / Scala 3.5.2 (their pin is 1.10.11/3.3.6)\\n- restore/save sbt cache keyed on build.sbt + .circleci/config.yml + project/build.properties + project/plugins.sbt (paths ~/.m2 ~/.ivy2/cache ~/.sbt)\\n- steps: checkout; run 'make check' via 'cat /dev/null | sbt scalafmtCheckAll test'; store_test_results from target/test-reports\\n- slack/notify on fail (optional, needs slack-secrets context)\\nDo NOT copy their test-integration/test-contracts jobs (no such tests here yet - see bad_usernames_api-0u3) or build-image/publish-image GCR jobs (belongs with Dockerfile bead bad_usernames_api-7he). Reference: gh api repos/flurdy/letterbox-scoring/contents/.circleci/config.yml\\n\",\"title\":\"Add CircleCI CI workflow\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"bad_usernames_api-au3\",\"title\":\"Add GitHub Actions CI workflow\",\"description\":\"No CI yet. Add .github/workflows that runs 'make check' (scalafmt check + sbt test) on push/PR against main. Gives 'make ci' something honest to point at and enables PR status gating.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"ivarabrahamsen@bluelightcard.co.uk\",\"created_at\":\"2026-07-03T12:25:37Z\",\"created_by\":\"Ivar Abrahamsen\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-07-03T12:25:37Z\",\"labels\":[\"ci\",\"milestone-1\"]}"}
